    <status value="extensions"/><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><p>This value set includes codes based on the following rules:</p><ul><li>Include these codes as defined in <code>http://va.gov/terminology/vistaDefinedTerms/52-100</code><table class="none"><tr><td style="white-space:nowrap"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b><a href="ConceptMap-CMVFOutMedRequestStatus.html">VF_OutMedRequestStatus</a></b></td></tr><tr><td>0</td><td>ACTIVE</td><td><span title="SOURCEISNARROWERTHANTARGET">&lt;</span><a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-medicationrequest-status.html#medicationrequest-status-active">active</a></td></tr><tr><td>NULL</td><td>ACTIVE</td><td><span title="SOURCEISNARROWERTHANTARGET">&lt;</span><a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-medicationrequest-status.html#medicationrequest-status-active">active</a></td></tr><tr><td>13</td><td>DELETED</td><td><span title="EQUIVALENT">~</span><a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-medicationrequest-status.html#medicationrequest-status-entered-in-error">entered-in-error</a></td></tr><tr><td>12</td><td>DISCONTINUED</td><td><span title="SOURCEISNARROWERTHANTARGET">&lt;</span><a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-medicationrequest-status.html#medicationrequest-status-stopped">stopped</a><br/><span title="SOURCEISNARROWERTHANTARGET">&lt;</span><a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-medicationrequest-status.html#medicationrequest-status-stopped">stopped</a></td></tr><tr><td>15</td><td>DISCONTINUED (EDIT)</td><td><span title="SOURCEISNARROWERTHANTARGET">&lt;</span><a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-medicationrequest-status.html#medicationrequest-status-stopped">stopped</a></td></tr><tr><td>14</td><td>DISCONTINUED BY PROVIDER</td><td><span title="SOURCEISNARROWERTHANTARGET">&lt;</span><a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-medicationrequest-status.html#medicationrequest-status-stopped">stopped</a></td></tr><tr><td>4</td><td>DRUG INTERACTIONS</td><td><span title="SOURCEISNARROWERTHANTARGET">&lt;</span><a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-medicationrequest-status.html#medicationrequest-status-draft">draft</a></td></tr><tr><td>11</td><td>EXPIRED</td><td><span title="EQUIVALENT">~</span><a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-medicationrequest-status.html#medicationrequest-status-completed">completed</a></td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td>HOLD</td><td><span title="SOURCEISNARROWERTHANTARGET">&lt;</span><a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-medicationrequest-status.html#medicationrequest-status-active">active</a></td></tr><tr><td>1</td><td>NON-VERIFIED</td><td><span title="SOURCEISNARROWERTHANTARGET">&lt;</span><a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-medicationrequest-status.html#medicationrequest-status-draft">draft</a></td></tr><tr><td>16</td><td>PROVIDER HOLD</td><td><span title="SOURCEISNARROWERTHANTARGET">&lt;</span><a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-medicationrequest-status.html#medicationrequest-status-active">active</a></td></tr><tr><td>5</td><td>SUSPENDED</td><td><span title="SOURCEISNARROWERTHANTARGET">&lt;</span><a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-medicationrequest-status.html#medicationrequest-status-active">active</a></td></tr></table></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-medicationrequest-status.html"><code>http://hl7.org/fhir/CodeSystem/medicationrequest-status</code></a><table class="none"><tr><td style="white-space:nowrap"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td><td><b><a href="ConceptMap-CMVFOutMedRequestStatus.html">VF_OutMedRequestStatus</a></b></td></tr><tr><td><a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-medicationrequest-status.html#medicationrequest-status-active">active</a></td><td>active</td><td>The prescription is 'actionable', but not all actions that are implied by it have occurred yet.</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-medicationrequest-status.html#medicationrequest-status-entered-in-error">entered-in-error</a></td><td>entered-in-error</td><td>Some of the actions that are implied by the medication request may have occurred.  For example, the medication may have been dispensed and the patient may have taken some of the medication.  Clinical decision support systems should take this status into account</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-medicationrequest-status.html#medicationrequest-status-stopped">stopped</a></td><td>stopped</td><td>Actions implied by the prescription are to be permanently halted, before all of the administrations occurred. This should not be used if the original order was entered in error</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-medicationrequest-status.html#medicationrequest-status-draft">draft</a></td><td>draft</td><td>The prescription is not yet 'actionable', e.g. it is a work in progress, requires sign-off, verification or needs to be run through decision support process.</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-medicationrequest-status.html#medicationrequest-status-completed">completed</a></td><td>completed</td><td>All actions that are implied by the prescription have occurred.</td><td/></tr></table></li></ul></div>
